aign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。</span>"},{"pid":"bf6fac4b608ed804793f9449488fa2ee45a90d12","tid":1672573,"uid":103913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5679638f4a867f8d82a3c703949b6429c52b184","tid":1672573,"uid":239516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec97a651eb9e2e866befe6d71e332ff642b21dd6","tid":1672573,"uid":103913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"叫樓豬搞又唔肯，然後老屈人唔撐新疆<br />\n惡撚過土共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"咪繼續shift focus囉你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同港共出手一樣都低<br />\n<br />\n你支持新疆集會係咁樣支持既咩？推個post都話 你搞咪推囉lo~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T08:42:10.000Z","msg":"實有人做搞手有人做支持者架啦<br />\n樓豬又唔肯踏出第一步，又諸多齮齕<br />\n正宗冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbcbaf8afde3ade53d79e